RollbackValidationForm is a Form
    Layout
        display as text
            visible when (RollbackValidationFailed)
                header3 of "<ConfigSnapshotItemInfo.Name>RollbackValidationStatus"
                single column
                    ConfigRollbackInfo.ConfigValidationStatus.Status
                        no label
                        display as tag
                            color of red
                    ConfigRollbackInfo.ConfigValidationStatus.ValidationErrorText
                        no label
            visible when (ConfigBundleSnapshot.RollbackConfigValidationStatus.Status.Failed)
                header3 of "OverallSnapshotRollbackValidationStatus"
                single column
                    ConfigBundleSnapshot.RollbackConfigValidationStatus.Status
                        no label
                        display as tag
                            color of red
                    ConfigBundleSnapshot.RollbackConfigValidationStatus.ValidationErrorText
                        no label
